# NONTON — Live TV & VOD (iptv-player)
#
# Required for TMDB integration:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_TMDB_API_KEY=your_read_access_token_here
# TMDB_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_read_access_token_here
#
# Get a free API key at: https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
#
# Without these keys, the curated movie dataset (40 titles) is used.
# With TMDB, you get full search, trending, and infinite catalog at build time.